[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0488","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0488.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0294","title":"Microsoft Windows WINS 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 的 WINS 服务存在安全漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 SNMP 协议向目标 WINS 服务器发送特制请求，删除 WINS 数据库中的所有记录，导致网络名称解析服务失效。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者无需认证即可利用 SNMP 管理接口实施拒绝服务攻击，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0294"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:05.503","remediation":"安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 5 或更高版本补丁，或升级至 Windows 2000 及以上版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙及主机层面限制 SNMP 服务 (UDP 161) 的访问来源，仅允许受信任的管理主机访问，并在 WINS 服务器上配置 SNMP 读写团体字串为复杂值，避免使用默认的 \"public\"。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0294","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20564","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0294.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0294","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0294.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0294.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0294.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g6mp-qfqw-f6cf/GHSA-g6mp-qfqw-f6cf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0294.json","https://github.com/CERTCC/SBOM/blob/ae581e32992458f65018df4eced684b7370bba39/SwiftBOM/cpe_lookup/cve_lookup/microsoft/wins_cve.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0488.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0458","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0458.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0272","title":"Slmail POP3 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Slmail 3.0.2421 及 2.5 版本的 POP3 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标主机的 POP3 端口（默认 110）发送特制恶意数据包，导致服务进程崩溃或停止响应，造成正常的邮件收发功能中断。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需复杂权限即可触发，影响运行 Slmail 服务的邮件服务器系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0272"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.843","remediation":"Slmail 产品已停止维护多年，建议迁移至现代受支持的邮件服务器软件（如 Postfix、Exchange 等）。如仍需继续使用，可在防火墙层面限制 POP3 端口（110）仅允许受信任 IP 段访问，并监控异常连接流量作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0272","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0272","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/1b69cf2313f68e29acceed58f52f6109cd37bb04/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-02xx/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/justakazh/CVE_Database/blob/06bd07f32c89b43f30d59ff450dfbb661e471cbe/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/2d2ea2d13a3a7facfa195486d4f9782c62a06518/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0272.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/e75163879b5629a697822216993d714626893061/api/1999/CVE-1999-0272.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0458.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0213","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0213.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0090","title":"IBM AIX rcp 命令本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 系统 rcp 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 rcp 命令提交超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存数据并获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。利用需要本地用户身份，成功利用后攻击者可完全控制目标系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0090"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.733","remediation":"IBM 已在 AIX 4.x 版本的 APAR IY09308 中修复此漏洞，建议更新 bos.rte.net_filesystem fileset 至包含该 APAR 的维护级别。临时缓解措施可移除 /usr/bin/rcp 的 setuid 权限：chmod u-s /usr/bin/rcp，或禁用 r-commands 服务（rshd、rexecd）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0090"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0213.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0363","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0363.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0182","title":"Samba Samba 1.9.19 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Samba 1.9.19 及更早版本存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经认证的远程攻击者可通过向 Samba 服务发送特制的超长密码字符串触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 Samba 1.9.19 的 Unix/Linux 系统，无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0182"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:46.523","remediation":"立即升级 Samba 至 2.0.0 及以上版本（1.9.19 系列已停止维护，2.0.0 修复了该缓冲区溢出问题）。如无法立即升级，可在 smb.conf 中设置 hosts allow/deny 限制可访问 SMB 服务的源 IP 范围，并在防火墙层面屏蔽 TCP 端口 139 和 445 的外部访问以临时缓解风险。现代 Linux 发行版应直接使用系统包管理器更新至当前受支持版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/h-110.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20308","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0182.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0182.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0182","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0182.json","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/2020/samba/gb_samba_CVE-1999-0182.nasl","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0182.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/292.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vc5j-x9w7-frw6/GHSA-vc5j-x9w7-frw6.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/jbeasl7/openvas-feed-sync-local/blob/02ed2a2b96fc19fd49a4be810f3493abb776ec4e/openvas-feeds/nvt-feed/2020/samba/gb_samba_CVE-1999-0182.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0363.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0470","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0470.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0282","title":"（已废弃）CVE-1999-0282 错误合并 SunOS loadmodule 两个独立漏洞的无效编号","description":"CVE-1999-0282 是一个已被官方驳回（REJECTED）的 CVE 编号，原因是它错误地将 CVE-1999-1584 和 CVE-1999-1586 两个不同漏洞的参考信息和描述合并为一条记录。NVD 已移除该编号下所有描述与引用，禁止继续使用。该编号不指向任何真实存在的漏洞，不存在可利用的攻击面或影响范围。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0282"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:56.640","remediation":"CVE-1999-0282 已被撤销，请勿使用此编号。实际漏洞分别对应 CVE-1999-1584（SunOS 4.1.1–4.1.3c 及 Open Windows 3.0 中 loadmodule/modload 的本地权限提升）和 CVE-1999-1586（SunOS 4.1.x 中 xnews 调用的 loadmodule 未正确清理环境变量导致本地提权）。Sun 当时发布了补丁（如 Sun patch 100124-01），CERT 也发布了公告 CA-1993-18，但这些补丁现已无法获取。由于 SunOS 4.x 早已停止支持，建议将仍在运行的 SunOS 4.1.x 系统迁移至受支持的操作系统（如 Solaris 11、Linux 或 \\*BSD），同时严格控制 setuid/setgid 二进制文件的权限以降低本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0470.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0452","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0452.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0267","title":"NCSA HTTPd 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NCSA HTTPd 1.3 版本存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区越界写入，进而实现远程命令执行。该漏洞影响 NCSA HTTPd 1.x 系列版本，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0267"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:02.227","remediation":"NCSA HTTPd 已停止维护多年，建议立即迁移至 Apache HTTP Server 2.4.x 或 Nginx 等现代 Web 服务器。迁移后需重新配置虚拟主机、访问控制和 SSL 证书，并关闭旧服务器上的 80/443 端口。如无法立即迁移，可在防火墙层面限制对 80 端口的访问来源 IP 作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0267","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/21050","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0267.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0267.json","https://github.com/geeknik/the-nuclei-templates/blob/36a6d14bce3293907a83afb498caec5fd45b1777/CVE-1999-0267.yaml","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0267","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0267.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-1999-0267.yaml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0267.md","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0267.json","https://github.com/lianqingsec/NucleiPocGather/blob/dcce204f62196117b9c95c52d8101ccf7a5d27bc/poc/cve/CVE-1999-0267.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0452.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0452.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0452.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0993","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0993.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0667","title":"TCP/IP ARP协议缓存投毒欺骗漏洞","description":"ARP（地址解析协议）协议设计上缺乏身份验证机制，在同一广播域内的任何攻击者均可向目标主机发送伪造的 ARP 应答报文，毒化其 ARP 缓存表，将目标 IP 地址与攻击者 MAC 地址关联。该漏洞影响所有使用 ARP 协议的网络设备，攻击者无需认证即可实施中间人攻击、IP 地址欺骗或拒绝服务攻击，是局域网中最基础且广泛存在的协议层安全问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0667"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-09-19T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.363","remediation":"在关键网段交换机启用动态 ARP 检测 (DAI) 和 DHCP Snooping，阻止伪造 ARP 报文；对核心资产配置静态 ARP 条目；部署 ARP 防火墙或 arpwatch 等监控工具检测异常 ARP 变化；使用 IPsec/MACsec 加密通信链路，降低中间人攻击风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602880019797&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0993.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0192","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0192.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0079","title":"Sun Solaris 7/8 FTP Server 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 7 和 Solaris 8 系统的 FTP 服务器存在资源耗尽漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标 FTP 服务发送大量 PASV 命令，导致服务器可用端口被迅速耗尽，从而使合法用户无法建立新的数据连接，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用门槛低，仅需网络可达即可触发，影响运行上述 Solaris 版本的系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0079"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-09-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.890","remediation":"建议安装 Sun 官方补丁 ID 106222-02 (Solaris 7) 或 106223-02 (Solaris 8)，限制单连接内 PASV 命令的并发端口数。也可在 in.ftpd 配置中降低 PASV 最小端口范围或缩短空闲端口超时。如无法升级，可在防火墙限制 FTP 控制连接速率作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0079"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0192.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0374","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0374.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0191","title":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 newdsn.exe 文件创建漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 的 newdsn.exe CGI 脚本存在文件创建/覆盖漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制 HTTP 请求利用此脚本，在服务器上任意创建或覆盖文件，可能导致系统配置被篡改或敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 IIS 3.0 版本，攻击复杂度较低，无需身份认证即可利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0191"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:51.367","remediation":"立即删除 IIS 3.0 服务器上的 newdsn.exe 文件或将其所在 cgi-bin 目录权限设置为禁止匿名访问；同时升级至 IIS 4.0 或更高版本以彻底消除该 CGI 脚本，或迁移至受支持的 Windows Server 版本并启用最新安全配置。若无法升级，在 Web 服务器层面配置 URL 过滤规则拦截对 newdsn.exe 的请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/275","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20309","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/1421f0a4349d5d46275cadd9c7c62349edf9c8bb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0191.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0191","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0191.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0191.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0191.json","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p6cp-hx87-7342/GHSA-p6cp-hx87-7342.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0191.yaml","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-iis.rules","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/N/newdsn.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0374.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0374.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0374.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0353","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0353.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0177","title":"O'Reilly WebSite 服务器远程代码执行漏洞","description":"WebSite Web 服务器中的 uploader 程序存在任意文件上传漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制的上传请求，将恶意可执行文件上传至服务器任意目录并远程执行，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响早期版本的 WebSite 服务器软件，攻击者只需能够网络访问目标服务器即可发起攻击，利用方式简单、危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0177"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:45.913","remediation":"建议立即升级至 O'Reilly WebSite Professional 2.x（该版本已修复 uploader 漏洞）；如无法升级，可直接删除或禁用 webroot 下的 uploader.exe/cgi 程序，并在 Web 服务器或防火墙层面限制对 uploader 相关路径的访问。由于该产品已终止技术支持（EOL），长期解决方案是迁移至仍在安全维护期的 Web 服务器（如 Apache、Nginx 或 IIS）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0177"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0353.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0258","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0258.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0115","title":"IBM AIX bugfiler 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 3.x 操作系统中的 bugfiler 程序存在任意文件创建漏洞，本地攻击者利用该程序可创建或覆盖系统文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 AIX 3.x 版本，攻击者仅需本地账户即可利用，无需用户交互，危害较高，CVSS 评分 7.2。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0115"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.230","remediation":"升级 AIX 系统至 4.1.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续发行版中修复。临时缓解措施：以 root 执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/bugfiler` 移除 setuid 特权位，防止本地用户通过 bugfiler 获取 root Shell；若无需使用 bugfiler 工具，可直接 `chmod 700 /usr/bin/bugfiler` 限制仅 root 可执行。请评估是否需同时更新 `bos.rte.security` 文件集的相关安全补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1800","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20290","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0115","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0115.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pf77-c4gh-6m4v/GHSA-pf77-c4gh-6m4v.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0258.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0081","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0081.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0024","title":"ISC BIND DNS 查询标识符可预测导致缓存投毒漏洞","description":"BIND DNS 服务器存在 DNS 缓存投毒漏洞，由于使用可预测的查询 ID 作为事务标识符，远程攻击者可通过向目标 DNS 服务器发送伪造的 DNS 响应报文，在无需认证的情况下实施缓存投毒攻击，将合法域名解析指向恶意 IP 地址，导致用户被重定向至恶意网站或遭受中间人攻击。该漏洞影响早期 BIND 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0024"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-08-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:22.577","remediation":"升级 BIND 至 4.9.7 或 8.2 及以上版本，该版本引入了随机化 DNS 查询 ID 机制，防止攻击者预测 ID 实施缓存投毒。若无法升级，可在 named.conf 中限制递归查询仅对受信任内部网段开放（allow-recursion），并在边界防火墙上阻断 UDP 53 端口的非授权外部访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0024"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0081.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0314","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0314.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0152","title":"Data General DG/UX finger 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"DG/UX 系统的 finger 服务程序存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标 finger 服务发送包含 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）的特制请求，利用服务程序对用户输入过滤不严的缺陷，在目标系统上以 finger 进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 DG/UX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，攻击复杂度低，利用方式简单，影响较为广泛。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0152"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-08-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:42.707","remediation":"立即禁用 finger 服务（/etc/inetd.conf 中注释 finger 行并重启 inetd），或在防火墙层面阻止外部对 finger 端口（79/tcp）的访问。由于 DG/UX 已停止技术支持且无官方补丁，建议迁移至受支持的现代操作系统以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0152"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0314.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0829","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0829.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0566","title":"IBM AIX syslog 日志填充拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 系统中的 syslog 组件存在日志写入权限缺陷，攻击者可从任意位置向 syslog 文件写入大量日志条目，导致磁盘空间被占满从而引发拒绝服务。同时，恶意日志会淹没正常审计记录，掩盖攻击者的操作痕迹，增加安全检测与溯源难度。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0566"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:39.053","remediation":"升级 IBM AIX 至 4.3.3 或更高版本，安装 APAR IX87386 补丁。同时配置 syslogd 限制远程写入（修改 /etc/syslog.conf 禁用非必要远程日志接收），在 /etc/hosts.allow 中限制 syslog 端口（UDP 514）的访问来源，并启用日志轮转（logrotate）防止单一日志文件过大导致磁盘写满。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0566","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0566","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0566.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7cvc-2mx4-55wc/GHSA-7cvc-2mx4-55wc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0566.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--8aeb4aa9-e098-4c64-a9a7-a80928b5b3b8.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0829.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0781","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0781.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0524","title":"Linux Kernel ICMP 时间戳和网络掩码信息泄露漏洞","description":"ICMP（互联网控制报文协议）地址掩码和时间戳响应可被任意主机触发，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统发送ICMP地址掩码请求或时间戳请求报文，从而获取目标网络的子网掩码、路由信息及系统时间等敏感数据。该漏洞广泛影响早期Linux内核版本及大量Unix类系统，攻击者可利用收集到的网络拓扑信息进行后续精准渗透攻击，属于信息泄露类漏洞，CVSS评分4.0，危害等级中危。通过操作系统层面禁用ICMP地址掩码和时间戳响应即可有效缓解。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0524"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:34.703","remediation":"在 `/etc/sysctl.conf` 中设置 `net.ipv4.icmp_echo_ignore_broadcasts=1` 并执行 `sysctl -p` 生效。使用 iptables 屏蔽入站 ICMP 时间戳请求 (`iptables -A INPUT -p icmp --icmp-type 13 -j DROP`) 和地址掩码请求 (`iptables -A INPUT -p icmp --icmp-type 17 -j DROP`)。如用 firewalld，执行 `firewall-cmd --permanent --direct --add-rule ipv4 filter INPUT 0 -p icmp --icmp-type timestamp-request -j DROP`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://descriptions.securescout.com/tc/11010","http://descriptions.securescout.com/tc/11011","http://kb.juniper.net/InfoCenter/index?page=content&id=JSA10705","http://kb.vmware.com/selfservice/microsites/search.do?cmd=displayKC&externalId=1434","http://www.osvdb.org/95","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/306","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/322","https://kc.mcafee.com/corporate/index?page=content&id=SB10053","https://support.f5.com/csp/article/K15277","https://github.com/noraj/ChronoLeak","https://github.com/threatlabindonesia/CVE-1999-0524-ICMP-Timestamp-and-Address-Mask-Request-Exploit","https://github.com/b1tsec/CVE-1999-0524","https://github.com/Ransc0rp1on/ICMP-Timestamp-POC"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0781.toml"}]